stories.text:
These past days Whatsapp (Meta) implemented a feature of reacting to messages on Whatsapp.

Isn't active in all devices yet, but some of those already do have it.

For those who already have it, what's your opinion about it?

To be honest, it freaks me out that an app of message service is implementing this feature, as it interfere of the role goal of Whatsapp - exchanging messages, easy and simple communication.
